@startuml
title FastAPI HTTP dependency resolution\nPlanned patient-summary endpoint using current Phase 4 dependencies

hide footbox
autonumber

actor "Client\nexternal caller" as Client

box "Runtime and HTTP interface" #AliceBlue
participant "Uvicorn\nASGI server" as Uvicorn
participant "FastAPI\nDependency Injection system" as FastAPI
participant "Planned patient-summary endpoint\ninterfaces/http/routers/patients.py\n[NOT IMPLEMENTED YET]" as Endpoint
end box

box "Security dependencies" #Lavender
participant "HTTPBearer\nFastAPI security utility" as Bearer
participant "get_jwt_token_verifier()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/security.py" as VerifierDependency
participant "get_current_principal()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/security.py" as PrincipalDependency
participant "JwtTokenVerifier\ninfrastructure/security/jwt_token_verifier.py" as Verifier
end box

box "Use-case dependencies" #HoneyDew
participant "get_patient_summary_use_case()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/use_cases.py" as UseCaseDependency
participant "GetPatientSummaryUseCase\napplication/use_cases/get_patient_summary.py" as UseCase
end box

box "Adapter dependencies" #Moccasin
participant "get_patient_reader()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/adapters.py" as PatientReaderDependency
participant "get_condition_reader()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/adapters.py" as ConditionReaderDependency
participant "get_encounter_reader()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/adapters.py" as EncounterReaderDependency
participant "get_observation_reader()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/adapters.py" as ObservationReaderDependency
end box

box "Database dependency" #LightCyan
participant "get_database_session()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/database.py" as DatabaseDependency
participant "get_session_factory()\ninterfaces/http/dependencies/database.py" as FactoryDependency
participant "app.state.session_factory\ninterfaces/http/app.py" as SessionFactory
participant "SQLAlchemy Session\nrequest-scoped object" as DatabaseSession
end box


note over FastAPI
FastAPI has already inspected the endpoint signature.

Conceptual parameters:

principal:
  Annotated[
    CurrentPrincipal,
    Depends(get_current_principal)
  ]

use_case:
  Annotated[
    GetPatientSummaryUseCase,
    Depends(get_patient_summary_use_case)
  ]
end note


Client -> Uvicorn: GET /patients/{patient_id}/summary\nAuthorization: Bearer <JWT>
Uvicorn -> FastAPI: Forward ASGI request

FastAPI -> FastAPI: Match route and build\nrequest dependency context

note over FastAPI, Endpoint
FastAPI does not call the endpoint yet.

It must resolve all required dependency
values before invoking the endpoint.
end note


group Resolve CurrentPrincipal branch

    FastAPI -> Bearer: Extract Authorization credentials

    Bearer --> FastAPI: HTTPAuthorizationCredentials

    FastAPI -> VerifierDependency: get_jwt_token_verifier(request)

    VerifierDependency -> VerifierDependency: Read request.app.state.jwt_token_verifier

    VerifierDependency --> FastAPI: shared JwtTokenVerifier

    FastAPI -> PrincipalDependency: get_current_principal(\ncredentials,\nverifier\n)

    PrincipalDependency -> Verifier: verify(raw_token)

    Verifier --> PrincipalDependency: VerifiedJwtClaims

    PrincipalDependency -> PrincipalDependency: Create CurrentPrincipal

    PrincipalDependency --> FastAPI: CurrentPrincipal P1

end


group Resolve GetPatientSummaryUseCase branch

    note over FastAPI
    get_patient_summary_use_case() cannot run yet.

    It first needs four reader adapters.
    end note


    group Resolve shared SQLAlchemy Session

        FastAPI -> DatabaseDependency: get_database_session(request)

        DatabaseDependency -> FactoryDependency: get_session_factory(request)

        FactoryDependency -> SessionFactory: Read request.app.state.session_factory

        SessionFactory --> FactoryDependency: sessionmaker

        FactoryDependency --> DatabaseDependency: sessionmaker

        DatabaseDependency -> SessionFactory: session_factory()

        SessionFactory -> DatabaseSession: Create Session S1

        DatabaseSession --> DatabaseDependency: Session S1

        DatabaseDependency --> FastAPI: yield Session S1

        note over FastAPI, DatabaseSession
        FastAPI stores Session S1 in the
        dependency cache for this request.

        The yield dependency remains suspended.

        Cleanup will happen after the endpoint
        and response processing finish.
        end note

    end


    group Resolve Patient reader

        FastAPI -> PatientReaderDependency: get_patient_reader(session=S1)

        PatientReaderDependency -> PatientReaderDependency: SqlAlchemyPatientReader(S1)

        PatientReaderDependency --> FastAPI: PatientReader PR1

    end


    group Resolve Condition reader

        FastAPI -> FastAPI: Same get_database_session requested\nReuse cached Session S1

        FastAPI -> ConditionReaderDependency: get_condition_reader(session=S1)

        ConditionReaderDependency -> ConditionReaderDependency: SqlAlchemyConditionReader(S1)

        ConditionReaderDependency --> FastAPI: ConditionReader CR1

    end


    group Resolve Encounter reader

        FastAPI -> FastAPI: Same get_database_session requested\nReuse cached Session S1

        FastAPI -> EncounterReaderDependency: get_encounter_reader(session=S1)

        EncounterReaderDependency -> EncounterReaderDependency: SqlAlchemyEncounterReader(S1)

        EncounterReaderDependency --> FastAPI: EncounterReader ER1

    end


    group Resolve Observation reader

        FastAPI -> FastAPI: Same get_database_session requested\nReuse cached Session S1

        FastAPI -> ObservationReaderDependency: get_observation_reader(session=S1)

        ObservationReaderDependency -> ObservationReaderDependency: SqlAlchemyObservationReader(S1)

        ObservationReaderDependency --> FastAPI: ObservationReader OR1

    end


    group Construct use case

        FastAPI -> UseCaseDependency: get_patient_summary_use_case(\npatient_reader=PR1,\ncondition_reader=CR1,\nencounter_reader=ER1,\nobservation_reader=OR1\n)

        UseCaseDependency -> UseCase: Create GetPatientSummaryUseCase

        UseCase --> UseCaseDependency: Use-case instance UC1

        UseCaseDependency --> FastAPI: GetPatientSummaryUseCase UC1

    end

end


note over FastAPI
FastAPI now has all values required
by the endpoint:

principal = P1
use_case = UC1
patient_id = value from path
end note


FastAPI -> Endpoint: get_patient_summary(\npatient_id,\nprincipal=P1,\nuse_case=UC1\n)

Endpoint -> UseCase: execute(patient_id)

note over UseCase, DatabaseSession
The use case calls its ports.

The four SQLAlchemy readers use
the same request-scoped Session S1.
end note

UseCase --> Endpoint: PatientSummary

Endpoint --> FastAPI: HTTP response data

FastAPI -> FastAPI: Serialize response


group Cleanup yield dependencies

    FastAPI -> DatabaseDependency: Resume after yield

    DatabaseDependency -> DatabaseSession: Exit context manager\nClose Session S1

    DatabaseSession --> DatabaseDependency: Session closed

    DatabaseDependency --> FastAPI: Dependency cleanup complete

end


FastAPI --> Uvicorn: HTTP 200 response
Uvicorn --> Client: Patient summary response


note over FastAPI
The visual order of sibling dependency
branches is explanatory.

The important rule is dependency order:

a dependency is executed only after
its own subdependencies are resolved.
end note

@enduml
